  "title": "Administrative Assistant (12-months)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Data entry, reports collation, filing &amp; documentation</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate premium calculation in relation to policy documentation</li>\n  <li>Maintain filing system and perform regular archiving of obsolete documents for off-site storage</li>\n  <li>Undertake any other assignments as allocated</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a recognised Diploma or higher qualifications</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant working experience will be advantageous</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Office365 Word and Excel applications</li>\n  <li>Accurate and meticulous</li>\n  <li>Ability to communicate effectively on the phone and through emails</li>\n  <li>Ability to work well in a team</li>\n  <li>Mature and able to work independently</li>\n</ul>",
